  ('medical-tech-moex-02988', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關吞噬細胞表面受體之敘述，何者正確？', '["Dectin-1及CR1（complement receptor 1）屬於C-type lectin的吞噬細胞表面接受體，能夠辨識包含黴 菌、細菌及病毒等病原體脂表面抗原成分", "MARCO（macrophage receptor with a collagenous structure）為scavenger receptors的成員，具有 fibronectin-like domain之三聚體構造特徵", "巨噬細胞表面接受體CD36能夠辨識病原體表面許多抗原性成分，但是並不包含長鏈脂肪酸（long-chain fatty acids）", "fMLF（formyl Met-Leu-Phe）receptor與C5a receptor屬於G-protein-coupled receptors之成員，能夠辨 識病原體表面抗原成分，促進殺菌能力"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6ed4be687229", "answer_pdf_sha1": "474e7978037e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "66", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02989', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關生發中心（germinal center）之敘述，何者正確？', '["淋巴濾泡（lymphoid follicles）包含生發中心構成初級淋巴濾泡（primary lymphoid follicles）", "生發中心的暗區（dark zone）由表現CXCR4及CXCR5的基質細胞（stromal cell）所構成", "生發中心的亮區（light zone）由表現CXCR4的生發中心母細胞（centroblasts）所構成", "B細胞能夠藉由CXCR4之表現與否在生發中心的暗區（dark zone）與亮區（light zone）來回進出"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6ed4be687229", "answer_pdf_sha1": "474e7978037e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "66", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
